{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>My Virtual Friend</strong> is the ultimate desktop companion, adding a touch of cuteness and relaxation to your daily work. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your virtual friend will keep you company as you go about your day. Take care of her to earn friendship tokens, which you can spend on customizing her wardrobe, backgrounds, and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/shopping.gif?t=1738234883\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With its transparent mode, the game blends seamlessly into your workspace, letting you stay productive without distraction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/transparency.gif?t=1738234883\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Adorable Companion</strong>: Cute girls doing cute things to cheer you up throughout your day.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customizable Character</strong>: Personalize your character\u2019s look and interact with her in meaningful ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Focus &amp; Relax</strong>: multiple unique instrumental music playlists designed to help you focus or relax while you work.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multi-Language Support</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/extras/angry.gif?t=1738234883\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738234883","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434800/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738234883","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.